The incident with the fake passport underscores the critical need for more sophisticated approaches to Know Your Customer (KYC) compliance, especially in the age of advanced AI. Multi-layered verification and real-time risk scoring are indeed essential steps.

Moreover, integrating human oversight is paramount; it ensures that automated systems do not overlook nuanced details or anomalies that might slip through otherwise.

